                                                                  Mini Project using Oops 


1. Bank Management System 

    Concepts Used: Inheritance, abstraction, encapsulation
    
    Features:
    
    Deposit/withdraw money
    
    Account balance
    
    Savings & Current accounts

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------xxxx------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. Library Management System 

    Concepts Used: Classes, inheritance, file handling, encapsulation.
    
    Features:
    
    Add/remove books
    
    Borrow/return books
    
    Track available books & members

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------xxxx------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. School Management System 

    Concepts Used: Inheritance, polymorphism, multiple classes
    
    Features:
    
    Teachers & Students
    
    Assign subjects
    
    Grade students

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------xxxx------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. Online Shopping System 

    Concepts Used: Inheritance, polymorphism, classes, encapsulation
    
    Features:
    
    Products with categories
    
    Cart system
    
    Checkout with total calculation

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------xxxx------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
